race.description: Aboriginal Family Legal Service QLD Handicap (Bm58)
race.comment: GREY NORTHERN (4) did a good job to score by 1.75L over this course and distance last start quickly back on track. Maps for the run of the race, and she's well placed to repeat the dose. Stablemate COUNTER (1) was outgraded at Doomben but was only beaten 2L there this trip prior in a 68. Just missed at Eagle Farm in that grade prior and despite top weight will be hard to roll in this company.  BAVARIAN LADY (7) has been busting to win for the Currie yard and she found GREY NORTHERN 1.7L too good last time as a $3 favourite. Has a key gear switch and is worth another chance. MUCHACHO (3) deserved his Maiden win here over a mile. Will position forward and from the paint will give himself every chance to see out the longer distance. Lightly raced with plenty of scope for improvement.
